### ========================================
### FUZZY SEARCH - USERS
### ========================================

### Search users by first name
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=John&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users by last name
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=Doe&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users by full name (first + last)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=John Doe&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users by email
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=john@example.com&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users by partial email
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=john&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users by phone number
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=1234567890&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users with role filter (only admins)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=admin&role_id=1&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users with role filter (only sub-admins)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=jane&role_id=2&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Search users with role filter (only candidates)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=candidate&role_id=3&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Fuzzy search with typo tolerance (e.g., "Jon" instead of "John")
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=Jon&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

