### ERROR TEST CASES
### ========================================

### Test: Search without authentication (should fail with 401)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=john&page=1&page_size=20

### Test: Empty search query (should fail with validation error)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/users?q=&page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Test: Invalid page number
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/candidates?q=test&page=0&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### Test: Invalid page size (too large)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/candidates?q=test&page=1&page_size=200
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

